title: TorchScript import/export using the ONNX protobuf format
body_html:
Notes:

  • we need to handle control-flow import/export correctly.
  • It is ok for now to throw module information away and just create a single method + initial values.
  • Import should be capable of running using C++ only, so that the op can run in a caffe2 network.

body:
Notes:
* we need to handle control-flow import/export correctly.
* It is ok for now to throw module information away and just create a single method + initial values.
* Import should be capable of running using C++ only, so that the op can run in a caffe2 network.
